=============================
== about research_related
=============================
> research_related is created to manage order of reading priority.
    : reading priority must match with long term and short term task
> reading list must contain expected deadline
    : This is important to create realistic plan

==============================
== Rule
==============================
> leaf folders must contain the following folder
    :read
    :not read
    :reading_list (in highest priority to lowest priority)
> research_paper may be belonged to more than 1 folder
    :one to many relationship
    :This is intended to enhances ease of finding wanted_research_paper.
>overview dir naming convention is as followed
    :overview
        >>name overview
            >>>name type1 (tags + papers)
            >>>name type2 (tags + papers)
        >>name2 overview
            ...